      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help but they only loved the version of me that succeeded. they loved the mask. now that the mask is broken, there's just nothing underneath. i feel like i'm just a ghost walking around in a body that doesn't belong to anyone anymore. it wouldn't even be a loss to them, it would just be... relief that the failure is gone.",
